embeds.title: AR Bundle: Augmented Reality — App & Game Templates, AR Plugins
embeds.description:
**AR Bundle — Complete Collection of AR Projects & AR Tools.**

Bundle includes the next 12 assets. After purchasing this bundle, visit each package listed below, add to your assets and you will be able to get them for free:

— AR Masks
— AR Toss Boss
— AR Survival Shooter
— AR Space Shooter
— AR Menu (AR Foundation: ARKit, ARCore)
— AR Menu (Vuforia)
— AR Basketball GO
— AR Throwing
— AR Camera GYRO
— AR + VR: MR Camera
— AR Camera ACCELEROMETER
— AR Shadow

**LIMITATIONS**
Learn Limitations for Each Asset separately.
